snippet: Hayley Wickenheiser set up two goals and goalie Shannon Szabados held on after a late brawl to help Canada beat the United States in the opening game of the pre-Olympic tour.
abstract: Canada women's hockey team beats United States, 3-2.
lead_paragraph: Hayley Wickenheiser set up two goals and goalie Shannon Szabados held on after a late brawl to help Canada beat the United States in the opening game of the pre-Olympic tour.

headline.main: Canada Defeats U.S. Women in Hockey
